  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background-color:rgb(35, 135, 75)\">Tyrion V</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> chapter</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_storm_of_swords\" title=\"A storm of swords\"><img alt=\"AStormOfSwords.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/24/AStormOfSwords.jpg/220px-AStormOfSwords.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"353\" class=\"thumbborder\" srcset=\"/images/2/24/AStormOfSwords.jpg 1.5x\" /></a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">POV</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Page</th><td>\n428 <small>UK HC</small> <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters_Table_of_contents\" title=\"Chapters Table of contents\">Other versions</a>)</small></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:rgb(35, 135, 75)\">Chapter chronology <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters\" title=\"Chapters\">All</a>)</small></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_32\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 32\">Tyrion IV</a><br />↑</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_37\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 37\">Jaime V</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">&#160;←</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle; padding-right:0.1em; padding-left:0.1em;\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Tyrion V</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">→&#160;</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_39\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 39\">Arya VII</a></td>\n</tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n↓<br /><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_53\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 53\">Tyrion VI</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Synopsis\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Synopsis</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Character_List_appearing.2Fmentioned\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character List appearing/mentioned</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Places_and_terms_mentioned\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Places and terms mentioned</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References_and_Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References and Notes</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Synopsis\">Synopsis</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_38&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Synopsis\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tleft\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:SmirtouilleThe_Red_Viper.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a9/SmirtouilleThe_Red_Viper.png/300px-SmirtouilleThe_Red_Viper.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a9/SmirtouilleThe_Red_Viper.png/450px-SmirtouilleThe_Red_Viper.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a9/SmirtouilleThe_Red_Viper.png/600px-SmirtouilleThe_Red_Viper.png 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:SmirtouilleThe_Red_Viper.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Oberyn and his <a href=\"/index.php/Sand_steed\" title=\"Sand steed\">sand steed</a> - by Smirtouille © FFG</div></div></div>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion</a> has been sent to greet the three hundred <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dornishmen</a> with a small retinue. However, he is shocked when he finds that the Dornishmen are being led by Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Oberyn_Martell\" title=\"Oberyn Martell\">Oberyn Martell</a> and not his brother, Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Doran_Martell\" title=\"Doran Martell\">Doran</a>. The Red Viper of Dorne has an infamous reputation for using poisoned weapons in battle. The man fought in the <a href=\"/index.php/Free_Cities\" title=\"Free Cities\">Free Cities</a> and even formed his own <a href=\"/index.php/Sellsword\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sellsword\">sellsword</a> company, he studied at the <a href=\"/index.php/Citadel\" title=\"Citadel\">Citadel</a> for a time, and most importantly, he crippled <a href=\"/index.php/Willas_Tyrell\" title=\"Willas Tyrell\">Willas Tyrell</a> in a tourney. Though this was years ago, it has never been forgotten by the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tyrell\" title=\"House Tyrell\">Tyrells</a>, who will not be happy that this man is attending the marriage of one of them. \n</p><p>The Red Viper tells Tyrion the story of how he and <a href=\"/index.php/Elia_Martell\" title=\"Elia Martell\">Elia</a> traveled to <a href=\"/index.php/Casterly_Rock\" title=\"Casterly Rock\">Casterly Rock</a> when Tyrion was an infant. It was just after the death of <a href=\"/index.php/Joanna_Lannister\" title=\"Joanna Lannister\">Joanna Lannister</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a> was in mourning and ignored the Martells. Oberyn and Elia were disappointed to find out that Tyrion was only a dwarf, after the stories they had heard about him being Tywin’s monster son. The Red Viper then gets down to the point, asking Tyrion, \"when will justice be served?\" He warns Tyrion that he does not mean to stop after killing <a href=\"/index.php/Gregor_Clegane\" title=\"Gregor Clegane\">Gregor Clegane</a>: \"Before he dies, the Enormity that Rides will tell me whence came his orders, please assure your lord father of that.\" But Tyrion has a more subtle warning: The <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">Lannisters</a> have tens of thousands of Tyrell men present as allies. And the Tyrells hate the Dornish, and especially Prince Oberyn for what he did to Willas.\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"Character_List_appearing/mentioned\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character_List_appearing.2Fmentioned\">Character List appearing/mentioned</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_38&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character List appearing/mentioned\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"column-count:3; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Oberyn_Martell\" title=\"Oberyn Martell\">Oberyn Martell</a> The Red Viper</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Doran_Martell\" title=\"Doran Martell\">Doran Martell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Willas_Tyrell\" title=\"Willas Tyrell\">Willas Tyrell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Elia_Martell\" title=\"Elia Martell\">Elia Martell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Joanna_Lannister\" title=\"Joanna Lannister\">Joanna Lannister</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Gregor_Clegane\" title=\"Gregor Clegane\">Gregor Clegane</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Flement_Brax\" title=\"Flement Brax\">Flement Brax</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Merlon_Crakehall\" title=\"Merlon Crakehall\">Merlon Crakehall</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Leo_Tyrell_(Longthorn)\" title=\"Leo Tyrell (Longthorn)\">Leo Tyrell (Longthorn)</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Places_and_terms_mentioned\">Places and terms mentioned</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_38&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Places and terms mentioned\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"column-count:3; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dornishmen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Free_Cities\" title=\"Free Cities\">Free Cities</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Sellsword\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sellsword\">Sellsword</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Citadel\" title=\"Citadel\">Citadel</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tyrell\" title=\"House Tyrell\">House Tyrell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Casterly_Rock\" title=\"Casterly Rock\">Casterly Rock</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References_and_Notes\">References and Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"m